	<ThoughtDef ParentName = "AK_Thought_Permanent">
		<defName>AK_Thought_Trait_Greythroat</defName>
		<requiredTraits>
			<li>AK_Trait_Greythroat</li>
		</requiredTraits>
		<stages>
			<li>
				<label>飞羽的倒影</label>
				<description>其实我知道，母亲把我送来的时候就已经疯了。我无法对她混沌的痛苦感同身受，但我能理解，因为我也靠着那股执念走到了今天。</description>
				<baseMoodEffect>-15</baseMoodEffect>
			</li>
		</stages>
	</ThoughtDef>

